description:
This installment of the Auditions series brings you a few more hot hopefuls that we've had the pleasure of filming. Actually, I have a new assistant photographer who has been helping out and it seems he has a real knack for making the guys feel comfortable.

Guy #1: Gay. A real cutie with sparkling eyes and a great smile. He had contacted us via the website expressing an interest in modeling (he's a top). Very nice guy with a great personality! I'm very anxious to get him back for more!

Guy #2: Bisexual — has a girlfriend. 18-year-old runner with a smooth body and nice ass. Said he's never been fucked and wants to try it.

Guy #3: Straight. His friend had sent us his picture. Lean, tight little body on this one!
title: Auditions 13
